               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors (erased); a few lines (alternating with black lines) on the incipit page of Texts I and II and of all sections of Text I; first word of each strophe of Text I-1; section numbers of Text I-5; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; Ethiopic numerals (in Text I-5) or their elements.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 is known as Mälkǝʿa śǝʿǝl "Image of the Icon" within the Mälkǝʿa gubaʾe "Collection of Images".</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of Mary (Texts I-5) are numbered (number 22 is missing). Some of the miracles are followed by a short hymn:</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ጽዋዓ፡ ልቡና፡ መለኮታዊ። ... (fol. 15vb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ገይበ፡ ወርቅ፡ ምቅዳሐ፡ ሀሊብ። ... (fol. 16va-vb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ባሕርየ፡ ዘአልብኪ፡ ሤጠ፡ ወተውላጠ። ... (fol. 19ra)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ሰዊተ፡ ወይን፡ ዘመዋዕለ፡ ቀሥም። ... (fol. 20rb-va)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ መጽሔት፡ ጽድልት፡ ዘኢትዴመኒ። ... (fol. 21rb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ በለሰ፡ ርጢን፡ ዘነጋሢ። ... (fol. 22rb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ መሠረተ፡ አሚን፡ ወፍጻሜ። ... (fol. 24rb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ጎሐ፡ ጽባሕ፡ ብርህት፡ እንተ፡ ወለድኪ፡ ፀሐየ። ... (fol. 28va)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በክልኤ፡ ማርያም፡ ጥዕምተ፡ ሰም፡ ሕይወተ፡ ዘለዓለም። ... (fol. 30va)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ልብስ፡ ንጽሕት፡ ዘኢትትወሀብ፡ ለዘኢትደልዎ። ... (fol. 33rb-va)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ በትረ፡ መንግሥት፡ ዘእምሥርወ፡ ይሁዳ። ... (fol. 35ra-rb)</note>
                     <note>- ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ሀገረ፡ ፀወን፡ ዘኢያንቀለቅል፡ መሠረታ። ... (fol. 49ra-rb)</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Short, rhymed subscriptio (supplication for the scribe) is written on fol. 100ra.</note>
